FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1782233278
OL,3,CChild rapist still on run as brothers
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FJailing Ilyas in his absence on
OL,7,FMonday, Judge Peter Hampton praised
OL,8,Fthe courage of the five women who gave
OL,9,Fevidence against him, saying their
OL,10,Fvoices had finally been heard and they
OL,11,Fhad been believed by jurors.
OL,13,FJudge Hampton contrasted this with the
OL,14,F"cowardice" shown by the defendant,
OL,15,Fwho fled to a different continent to
OL,16,Favoid justice while he was on bail.
OL,18,FThe judge said Ilyas "took the
OL,19,Fcoward's route and fled".
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@KO]zD@VOU{D@XO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
