PN,33403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1782233278
OL,3,CChild rapist still on run as brothers
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FHe said: "He continues to try and
OL,7,Fmanipulate the proceedings from
OL,8,Fabroad, having his counsel espouse his
OL,9,Fgood work for the community whilst
OL,10,Fsimultaneously cowering from these
OL,11,Fproceedings in a different
OL,12,Fjurisdiction."
OL,14,FThe judge urged the authorities to use
OL,15,F"all means" to bring him back to the
OL,16,FUK.
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@NO]wD@AOUwD@KO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/14
