PN,33404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1782233278
OL,3,CChild rapist still on run as brothers
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FDetectives from the National Crime
OL,7,FAgency (NCA) have described how Ilyas
OL,8,Fsubjected one child to "three years of
OL,9,Frelentless torment and rape" from the
OL,10,Fage of 12.
OL,12,FIlyas was found guilty of raping four
OL,13,Fvictims and sexually abusing a fifth
OL,14,Fin September 2025, and two of his
OL,15,Fbrothers, Kamar and Kamran Ilyas, were
OL,16,Ffound guilty earlier this year of a
OL,17,Fstring of offences in relation to one
OL,18,Fof the girls Amar raped.
OL,26,@pD@XOUqD@\O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/14
