PN,33405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1782233278
OL,3,CChild rapist still on run as brothers
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FOn Monday, Kamar Ilyas was jailed for
OL,7,F10 years and Kamran Ilyas for three
OL,8,Fyears.
OL,10,FThe brothers were arrested as part of
OL,11,Fthe NCA's Operation Stovewood, which
OL,12,Fis the huge investigation into child
OL,13,Fsexual exploitation in Rotherham
OL,14,Fbetween 1997 and 2013, although this
OL,15,Foffending mainly took place in nearby
OL,16,FSheffield.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
