PN,33406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1782233278
OL,3,CChild rapist still on run as brothers
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FJudge Hampton told the defendants:
OL,7,F"Your victims were targeted,
OL,8,Fsexualised and, in some cases,
OL,9,Fsubjected to acts of a degrading and
OL,10,Fviolent nature."
OL,12,FAnd the judge added: "They were naive
OL,13,Fand young, reaching adolescence and
OL,14,Fsusceptible to the attention that was
OL,15,Fgiven to them.
OL,17,F"Some were groomed, some coerced and
OL,18,Fintimidated and some violently raped."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@PO]tD@VOUyD@AOUzD@fO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/14
