PN,33407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1782233278
OL,3,CChild rapist still on run as brothers
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FJudge Hampton said: "They showed
OL,7,Fimmeasurable courage in giving
OL,8,Fevidence."
OL,10,FAfter reading again some of the impact
OL,11,Fstatement of one of the victims, the
OL,12,Fjudge said: "She and the other four
OL,13,Fcomplainants have now been listened to
OL,14,Fby these juries.
OL,16,F"They have now been believed."
OL,18,FEarlier that complainant read her
OL,19,Fstatement to the court.
OL,26,@nD@UOUpD@JO]tD@MOUxD@AOUxD@^O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/14
