PN,33409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1782233278
OL,3,CChild rapist still on run as brothers
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FThe woman said: "What they did to me
OL,7,Fdidn't end when the abuse stopped.
OL,8,FIt's shaped every year of my life
OL,9,Fsince."
OL,11,FIn a statement read to the court,
OL,12,Fanother victim said: "No child should
OL,13,Fever have to go through what I did."
OL,15,FAnd, in a further read statement, a
OL,16,Fthird victim said: "I am a survivor
OL,17,Fand you are a coward."
OL,19,FA fourth complainant said: "I hope you
OL,20,Fgo to hell for what you did to me."
OL,26,@nD@QOUqD@GO]tD@VOUuD@dO]xD@TOUyD@VO]{D@
OL,26,A\OU|D@cO]
