OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1782233278
OL,3,CChild rapist still on run as brothers
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FAmar Ilyas, 41, was convicted of five
OL,7,Fcounts of rape of a child under 13,
OL,8,Fnine counts of rape, two counts of
OL,9,Fsexual activity with a child, three
OL,10,Fcounts of indecent assault and one
OL,11,Fcount of possession of an imitation
OL,12,Ffirearm with the intent of causing
OL,13,Ffear of violence.
OL,15,FThese were committed between 2004 and
OL,16,F2007, when he was 19 to 22.
OL,18,FKamar Ilyas, 39, was convicted of one
OL,19,Foffence of rape of a child under 13
OL,20,Fand two offences of sexual activity
OL,21,Fwith a child.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
