FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1782233278
OL,3,CChild rapist still on run as brothers
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FThese were committed between 2004-2006
OL,7,Fwhen he was 17 to 20.
OL,9,FKamran Ilyas, 38, was convicted of two
OL,10,Foffences of sexual activity with a
OL,11,Fchild.
OL,13,FThese were committed in 2004 when he
OL,14,Fwas 17.
OL,16,FMore than 50 people have been
OL,17,Fconvicted after investigations under
OL,18,FOperation Stovewood, which the NCA
OL,19,Fsays is the largest law enforcement
OL,20,Foperation of its kind in the UK.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
