PN,33412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1782233278
OL,3,CChild rapist still on run as brothers
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FStovewood has identified more than
OL,7,F1,100 children involved in
OL,8,Fexploitation between 1997 and 2013,
OL,9,Fand previous estimates have put its
OL,10,Fcost at about #90 million.
OL,12,FNCA senior investigating officer Alan
OL,13,FHastings said: "The court heard loud
OL,14,Fand clear from the women how the Ilyas
OL,15,Fbrothers inflicted devastating
OL,16,Fsuffering upon them, suffering which
OL,17,Faffects them to this day."
OL,26,@uD@POUyD@ZO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/14
