PN,33413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1782233278
OL,3,CChild rapist still on run as brothers
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FMartin McRobb, specialist prosecutor
OL,7,Ffor the Crown Prosecution Service,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The brothers Amar Ilyas, Kamar
OL,9,FIlyas and Kamran Ilyas groomed a young
OL,10,Fgirl with alcohol and drugs.
OL,12,F"They each sexually abused by preying
OL,13,Fon her vulnerability, causing her
OL,14,Fserious and lifelong harm.
OL,16,F"Amar Ilyas targeted four other young
OL,17,Fgirls and subjected them all to the
OL,18,Fmost horrendous acts of rape and
OL,19,Fsexual assault.
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G13/14
